                        <h2>Python</h2>
                        <p>This course introduces students to Python, a high-level, versatile programming language known for its simplicity and readability. Students will learn the fundamental programming concepts including variables, data types, control flow (loops, conditionals), functions, and object-oriented programming (OOP). The course will also cover Pythonâ€™s extensive standard library, data structures (lists, dictionaries, sets), and basic file handling.</p>
